Code preview of 款项计划信息表sl_fund_intent

drop table if exists sl_fund_intent;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_fund_intent */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_fund_intent
(
fundIntentId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
projectId bigint(20),
fundType smallint(6) not null comment '资金类型 (贷款：贷款贷出、贷款收息、贷款收本、贷款佣金支付)(融资：融资借入、融资付息、融资付本，融资佣金支付)',
intentDate datetime not null comment '计划到帐日',
payMoney numeric(10,2) comment '支出金额',
incomeMoney numeric(10,2) comment '收入金额',
factDate datetime comment '实际到帐日/实际还款日',
afterMoney numeric(10,2) comment '已对帐金额',
notMoney numeric(10,2) comment '未对帐金额',
isOverdue char(10) comment '是否逾期',
accrualMoney numeric(10,2) comment '逾期利息总额',
isFlat smallint(6) comment '是否平帐',
flatMoney numeric(10,2) comment '平帐金额',
remark tinytext comment '备注',
primary key (fundIntentId)
);

alter table sl_fund_intent comment '款项计划信息表';

alter table sl_fund_intent add constraint FK_FK_FUNDINTENT_SMALL_REC foreign key (projectId)
references sl_smallloan_project (projectId) on delete restrict on update restrict;
